{
  "stem": "18575.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandmother as I recalled, her first name was Pesah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, ?] grandfather was Godel, G-O-D-E-L.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "P as in Peter, E-S-A-H.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had good relation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I had constant fight with kids, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a great amount of anti-Semitism in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I myself was very much Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the way, our family was in Poland since 14th century.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had dates going back, and back, and back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, in any other country, anybody living that long would be considered a citizen, a part, you know, [? in ?] France, or Britain, or United States.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not so in Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You are not a Pole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Although I was a Pole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I spoke only Polish language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I love the literature.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'm sort of a patriot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not withstanding that, the kids were thought, both in school, in parochial school, to which I also went, by the way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I went to a Catholic parochial school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Taught all the-- by the-- by the church, the Christ killers, the [INAUDIBLE], the killers, the father killers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And anti-Semitism was almost inbred, almost, by osmosis passed on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we had fight with the kids, not with the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
